1
00:00:26,860 --> 00:00:30,780
=Criminal Scene=

2
00:00:31,300 --> 00:00:36,260
=Episode 4=

3
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:38,160
(Command Center)

4
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:41,620
Hello?

5
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:45,190
What?

6
00:00:46,620 --> 00:00:47,870
A dead body at the bar?

7
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:54,660
(Branch Commander's Office)

8
00:01:30,550 --> 00:01:31,100
Su Qian,

9
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,840
Any findings about the victim?

10
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:34,340
Rigor mortis has set in.

11
00:01:34,570 --> 00:01:36,580
Estimated time of death
was two to three hours ago.

12
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:38,150
It's 6:30 AM now.

13
00:01:38,340 --> 00:01:40,620
So that puts the time of death
at around 3 or 4 AM.

14
00:01:41,270 --> 00:01:42,940
Based on the angle of the wounds,

15
00:01:43,060 --> 00:01:45,820
the attacker likely struck from behind.

16
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:14,380
(Lei Wei, Bar Owner)
I wasn't at the scene.

17
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:16,190
I was drinking in a private room

18
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:18,060
when I suddenly heard people shouting

19
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:18,750
about a death.

20
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,750
So I went out to check

21
00:02:19,990 --> 00:02:21,620
and there he was.

22
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:23,620
And you?

23
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:25,660
Last night was hectic.

24
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:26,620
Five of us were working

25
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:28,100
and swamped.

26
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:30,270
You're the bar owner, right?

27
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:31,310
Yes.

28
00:02:32,100 --> 00:02:33,340
Tell me what happened.

29
00:02:34,220 --> 00:02:36,190
Well, someone threatened
to kill him last night.

30
00:02:36,190 --> 00:02:37,990
I didn't expect him
to end up dead for real.

31
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:43,990
Captain Gu!

32
00:02:44,990 --> 00:02:45,590
I'm here!

33
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:46,590
I'm already here!

34
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:48,270
Sorry,

35
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:49,900
I came late.

36
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:51,900
I got stuck in traffic.

37
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:53,500
Maybe when you

38
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,430
ditch your big SUV
for an electric scooter,

39
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:56,590
you won't be late.

40
00:02:58,310 --> 00:02:58,900
All right.

41
00:02:59,990 --> 00:03:00,470
Now,

42
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,150
back to the case.

43
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:03,990
You guys

44
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:05,100
won't believe this.

45
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:06,340
A female university student

46
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:08,470
barged in and attacked Matteo.

47
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:10,710
I remember Matteo saying,

48
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:12,430
"If I die tonight,

49
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,380
it's that crazy Jiang Xiaotang
who did it."

50
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:32,780
(People's Public Security)

51
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:42,670
Geezer Gu...

52
00:03:43,380 --> 00:03:44,380
Just cooperate.

53
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:50,500
(Forensic Studio)

54
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:01,750
Don't be nervous.

55
00:04:02,230 --> 00:04:02,940
You should know

56
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:04,940
that dealing with the living
is actually harder.

57
00:04:04,940 --> 00:04:05,380
No,

58
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,620
I'm not nervous.

59
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:16,100
Have you identified the victim?

60
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:17,310
Lei Wei said

61
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:19,310
he only knew the victim's English name,

62
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,260
Matteo.

63
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:21,820
He was a regular there.

64
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:23,020
Matteo, huh?

65
00:04:24,230 --> 00:04:25,550
English names are tricky to track.

66
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:27,500
Lei Wei said

67
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,580
the victim went there every week

68
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:32,260
and was always with a different girl.

69
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:37,430
Wait, it's him?

70
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:39,460
You know him?

71
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:41,990
Well, not personally.

72
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:42,700
But I know of him.

73
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,310
Just get to the point.

74
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:46,190
His real name was Liu Ang.

75
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:49,910
He was an art instructor
at an adult education center,

76
00:04:50,260 --> 00:04:52,110
specializing in figure drawing.

77
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,820
His artwork often depicted women

78
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:55,820
with a kind of melancholic charm.

79
00:04:56,060 --> 00:04:58,820
He's regarded as the contemporary artist
who understands women best.

80
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:01,230
Like so-called women's best friend.

81
00:05:01,550 --> 00:05:02,580
So he was quite popular.

82
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,200
Open your mouth.

83
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:29,910
Geezer Gu.

84
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:31,260
Captain Gu,

85
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:32,700
you shouldn't be here.

86
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,190
Okay.

87
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:38,140
Captain Gu,

88
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:41,190
the suspect is your girlfriend's sister.

89
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:42,430
Even though you're not related,

90
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:44,060
you should recuse yourself.

91
00:05:44,060 --> 00:05:44,500
No,

92
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:46,260
we already broke up.

93
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:47,340
Still, best recuse yourself.

94
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:50,990
Captain Gu,

95
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:52,550
don't take it personally.

96
00:05:53,550 --> 00:05:54,500
Xiaotang...

97
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:56,990
She is just going
through standard procedures.

98
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,990
There's no solid evidence
against her yet.

99
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:00,380
So don't worry.

100
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,190
Yue.

101
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:12,550
Be serious.

102
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,310
Jiang Xiaotang,

103
00:06:19,740 --> 00:06:21,280
what was your relationship with Liu Ang?

104
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:25,940
He was kind of my ex-boyfriend.

105
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:28,060
Did you say in the bar

106
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,140
you'd kill him?

107
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,430
Yes, I did.

108
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,033
(Q: Did you say in the bar
you'd kill him?)

109
00:06:39,034 --> 00:06:39,780
(A: Yes, I did.)

110
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:44,380
Welcome!

111
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:46,140
Have a good time tonight!

112
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:56,790
Excuse me.

113
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:57,540
Gotta do something.

114
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:04,910
Hey, ladies.

115
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,140
Do you want to have fun with us?

116
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:08,230
Go away.

117
00:07:09,550 --> 00:07:10,060
Let's go.

118
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:25,190
Oh...

119
00:07:25,350 --> 00:07:26,430
You've been working overtime

120
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:28,190
with another woman, huh?

121
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,910
You piece of trash!

122
00:07:29,910 --> 00:07:30,550
Stop it!

123
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:31,100
Xiaotang!

124
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:31,940
You trash!

125
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:32,820
Stop it.

126
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,310
You think I won't hit you, a woman?

127
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:36,940
Fine!

128
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:39,550
Let's see who takes who down first!

129
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:40,550
Stop hitting...

130
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:41,790
What are you doing?

131
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:42,740
Stay out of this!

132
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:45,460
Just stop it already!

133
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,980
I'm going to kill you today!

134
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:51,180
(Weili Bar)

135
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:00,860
Everyone saw that.

136
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,220
If I die, it's that crazy

137
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:04,100
Jiang Xiaotang who did it!

138
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:05,190
Listen here.

139
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:08,030
We can't both exist in the same world.
It's either me or you!

140
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:08,630
Miss.

141
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:09,340
Crazy!

142
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:09,700
Come.

143
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:10,520
- Leave.
- Let's go.

144
00:08:10,940 --> 00:08:11,700
I'll kill you!

145
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:12,190
Leave.

146
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:13,670
Let's go.

147
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,580
Where did you go

148
00:08:16,790 --> 00:08:17,510
after that?

149
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:19,700
I...

150
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,630
I wandered around the streets.

151
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:24,790
Was anyone with you?

152
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:27,340
Anna followed me at first.

153
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,340
But she was annoying so I left her.

154
00:08:29,340 --> 00:08:31,390
(Danger: High Voltage)
Xiaotang! Xiaotang!

155
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,860
Xiaotang, let's just go back, okay?

156
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:33,940
Leave me alone.

157
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:34,940
You can go if you want.

158
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:36,150
Xiaotang.

159
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:37,510
Xiaotang!

160
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:38,860
Come with me.

161
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:41,670
Leave me alone. Just go home.

162
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:42,580
Xiaotang.

163
00:10:06,270 --> 00:10:06,860
Help!

164
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:12,550
Help me!

165
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,670
Oh, Earth Mother.

166
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:19,030
Let my son return to me.

167
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:20,510
Help, madam!

168
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:24,150
Come back.

169
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:28,310
Come back.

170
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:31,550
Oh, Heavenly Father.

171
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:32,550
Help!

172
00:10:34,940 --> 00:10:36,310
Madam, help me!

173
00:10:36,310 --> 00:10:37,100
Dead?

174
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:39,460
Help!

175
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,340
Whose son died?

176
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:45,980
My son died?

177
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:47,550
Why him?

178
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:48,460
Why not you?

179
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,580
Help me, madam.

180
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:52,630
You should just die.

181
00:10:53,190 --> 00:10:55,700
Then you can marry my son
in the afterlife.

182
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,910
Be his wife.

183
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:06,270
(Women's Bathroom)

184
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:10,150
(I was out of it
and someone pushed me into the river.)

185
00:11:10,150 --> 00:11:11,270
(My clothes got all dirty.)

186
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:14,580
I can't believe someone pushed me.

187
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,390
(I went to a restroom to clean up.)

188
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,150
(When I was done,
it was already morning.)

189
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:22,580
Look.

190
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:24,550
There are still mud stains
on my clothes.

191
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:27,860
My hands are scraped too.

192
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:30,430
And after that?

193
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:36,100
The school gate opened,
so I went straight to class.

194
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:37,910
Why didn't you go home?

195
00:11:43,310 --> 00:11:43,860
I...

196
00:11:46,190 --> 00:11:47,150
I don't have a home

197
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:47,910
to go back to.

198
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,190
Otherwise, I wouldn't

199
00:11:49,190 --> 00:11:50,700
have ended up dating a loser like him.

200
00:11:53,190 --> 00:11:55,550
Is he accusing me of assault?

201
00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:56,220
Listen,

202
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:57,460
we fought each other.

203
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,670
If you're arresting me,

204
00:11:58,670 --> 00:12:00,310
it's only fair if you arrest him too.

205
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:01,860
He's already dead.

206
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,790
I want to see Geezer Gu.

207
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:17,550
Captain Gu.

208
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:25,580
Rubai.

209
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:27,580
Can I have a few minutes?

210
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,340
Just a quick word.

211
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:29,340
Did you forget

212
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:30,460
the "Recusal Principle?

213
00:12:30,580 --> 00:12:31,390
I know the rules.

214
00:12:31,650 --> 00:12:33,270
I won't interfere
with the investigation.

215
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:35,220
I only want to provide
some personal details

216
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:37,060
about Xiaotang as a witness.

217
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:38,740
Maybe it'll help you.

218
00:12:39,580 --> 00:12:41,080
(Forensic Studio)
Bringing personal feelings

219
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,060
into an investigation is a big taboo.

220
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:43,980
Look at you.

221
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:45,580
Your emotions are all over your face.

222
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:47,860
What?

223
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:49,940
I'm not like Kong Rubai,

224
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,460
wearing a long face all day.

225
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:52,860
Like the world owes him something.

226
00:12:55,310 --> 00:12:56,790
He died from a single stab wound.

227
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:59,030
The attacker was precise and efficient.

228
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:01,190
The weapon

229
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:04,030
was likely a short knife,
around 20 cm long.

230
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,510
Also,

231
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:07,580
the victim had a high alcohol level
in his blood.

232
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,390
There's one more thing.

233
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,630
The victim had late-stage

234
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:11,860
liver cancer.

235
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:13,100
Less than six months to live.

236
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:15,670
Liver cancer
and he was still drinking that much?

237
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:17,860
The symptoms aren't obvious at first.

238
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:20,150
The patient would only

239
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:21,670
feel fatigue and loss of appetite

240
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:23,100
without obvious discomfort.

241
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:24,910
There's a good chance

242
00:13:25,190 --> 00:13:26,940
Liu Ang didn't even know

243
00:13:26,940 --> 00:13:27,940
he had liver cancer.

244
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:30,340
His wallet, watch, and other valuables

245
00:13:30,340 --> 00:13:31,270
weren't taken.

246
00:13:32,430 --> 00:13:33,630
So it wasn't a robbery.

247
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:35,790
If

248
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:38,030
the killer knew

249
00:13:38,030 --> 00:13:39,460
the target was already dying,

250
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:40,550
how'd they feel?

251
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:44,790
Found the murder weapon?

252
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:45,630
Not yet.

253
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:50,100
The killer was left-handed.

254
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:52,630
But Xiaotang is right-handed.

255
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:54,630
Doesn't that mean she's...

256
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:57,670
It takes a lot of strength

257
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,430
to ambush and control

258
00:13:59,430 --> 00:14:00,820
a grown man from behind.

259
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:03,220
A girl like Xiaotang

260
00:14:03,430 --> 00:14:04,670
would struggle with that.

261
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:05,820
Of course,

262
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:06,740
it's just speculation,

263
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:07,460
not solid proof.

264
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,580
When the killer made his move
on Liu Ang,

265
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,220
the stab severed an artery,

266
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:16,430
meaning the victim's blood

267
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:17,940
would have sprayed out instantly.

268
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:19,860
If that's the case,

269
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:21,430
there should be bloodstains

270
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:23,510
on the killer's sleeves.

271
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:25,100
I'll check the security footage

272
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,150
to track Xiaotang's movements
last night.

273
00:14:28,820 --> 00:14:29,510
No need.

274
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:30,580
I sent someone to do it.

275
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:31,460
We'll know it soon.

276
00:14:32,270 --> 00:14:33,130
When did you get here?

277
00:14:33,340 --> 00:14:33,940
Just now.

278
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:36,030
So you heard everything?

279
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:39,460
But don't you think this suit lining
is a little too fancy?

280
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,150
Are all men's suits

281
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,150
this flashy inside?

282
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:45,550
Wow, this is good stuff.

283
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:47,100
What do you mean?

284
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:47,980
Let me take a look.

285
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,670
The lining of this suit

286
00:14:50,670 --> 00:14:52,220
is a Van Gogh painting.

287
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:53,430
This

288
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,940
has to be custom-made

289
00:14:55,940 --> 00:14:57,430
at a specialty fabric manufacturer.

290
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:58,980
The fabric, lining,

291
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:02,150
and buttons of this suit

