00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:04,630
are all custom-made and high-end.

293
00:15:05,860 --> 00:15:06,860
Give me an estimate.

294
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:09,740
Five thousand yuan?

295
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:10,700
Add another zero.

296
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:14,910
That's way too extravagant

297
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:15,980
for an instructor.

298
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:17,630
And this shirt

299
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,740
is high-thread-count Egyptian cotton.

300
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:21,100
It's custom-made

301
00:15:21,100 --> 00:15:22,350
from the same store as the suit.

302
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:24,100
How much for the shirt?

303
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:25,100
Around fifteen thousand,

304
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:26,510
maybe more.

305
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:29,820
Seems like our instructor
was living large.

306
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:32,940
Where did he get the money for all this?

307
00:15:33,860 --> 00:15:35,630
I don't know where the money came from.

308
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:38,270
But I think I know where the store is.

309
00:15:39,190 --> 00:15:40,820
Heavenly Father...

310
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,550
Earth Mother...

311
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:47,030
Please let my son

312
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:49,940
come home.

313
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:52,190
Heavenly Father...

314
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:55,150
Earth Mother...

315
00:15:57,100 --> 00:15:59,150
Please let my son

316
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,430
come home.

317
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:10,670
Son,

318
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:14,460
come home.

319
00:16:15,670 --> 00:16:16,300
Miss.

320
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:18,460
Wake up, miss.

321
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:23,540
Pale Reaper has killed someone!

322
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:24,540
Pale Reaper!

323
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:28,070
Pale Reaper has killed someone!

324
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:33,940
Move and stay put.

325
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:34,830
I didn't do it.

326
00:16:35,590 --> 00:16:36,740
- Behave.
- I didn't do it.

327
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:37,460
Stop struggling!

328
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:43,220
We searched the whole bar.

329
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:44,220
But just miss this spot.

330
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,270
Then another body turns up.

331
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:46,830
The timing is too perfect.

332
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:50,260
Captain Gu,

333
00:16:58,220 --> 00:16:59,870
the role-playing show
doesn't disappoint.

334
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:01,300
Either there are no murders,

335
00:17:01,430 --> 00:17:02,540
or there are two at once.

336
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:06,150
No coat in this weather,

337
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:07,350
no bag either.

338
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:10,430
That means they were either disposed of

339
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:12,590
or dumped somewhere else.

340
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,780
Or the victim wasn't killed here.

341
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:19,190
Back shows postmortem staining,

342
00:17:19,630 --> 00:17:20,940
meaning she was lying down

343
00:17:21,070 --> 00:17:22,150
after her death.

344
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:23,460
So it means

345
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:26,110
she was likely moved here later.

346
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,540
This could be a body dump site.

347
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,150
It's possible.

348
00:17:30,630 --> 00:17:31,940
But we need more evidence.

349
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:35,500
Bleeding in the eyes,

350
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:37,980
damage to the mouth's inner lining,

351
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:40,020
facial swelling, and pale discoloration

352
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,350
around the nose and mouth.

353
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:44,110
Her mouth and nose
were most likely covered,

354
00:17:44,110 --> 00:17:45,350
which led to suffocation.

355
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:45,830
(Forensic)

356
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:48,020
We'll need further tests to confirm.

357
00:17:51,190 --> 00:17:52,300
Missing half a fingernail.

358
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,980
Looks like she fought back hard

359
00:17:54,980 --> 00:17:56,500
before she died.

360
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:00,220
The lividity is starting to blur.

361
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:01,940
There's mild clouding in the corneas.

362
00:18:02,260 --> 00:18:03,910
The victim has been dead

363
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:05,590
for about twelve hours.

364
00:18:06,390 --> 00:18:07,940
She was likely killed around dawn.

365
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:14,940
There are marks
on her wrists and ankles.

366
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:16,940
It looks like she was tied up

367
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:17,970
before being brought here.

368
00:18:18,590 --> 00:18:20,110
Killing her out of hate is one thing.

369
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:22,270
But posing the body so delicately...

370
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:26,110
Could it be love?

371
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:28,430
Loving her, then killing her.

372
00:18:28,830 --> 00:18:31,780
After death, dumping her here.

373
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:36,460
Pale Reaper will take you all

374
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:38,500
and drag you to hell

375
00:18:39,630 --> 00:18:42,190
to climb the Mountain of Blades
and sink into the Boiling Oil.

376
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:44,910
Meet your doom!

377
00:18:57,780 --> 00:18:58,910
Anyone who comes to my store

378
00:18:59,590 --> 00:19:00,670
is my client.

379
00:19:01,260 --> 00:19:02,980
And my clients' information

380
00:19:03,430 --> 00:19:05,150
is something I must protect.

381
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,500
They come here for custom suits,

382
00:19:07,910 --> 00:19:10,070
spending more time and money

383
00:19:10,070 --> 00:19:11,830
than they would
on an off-the-rack piece.

384
00:19:12,220 --> 00:19:13,940
That's not so I can gossip about them.

385
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:16,190
But the problem is,

386
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:19,500
one of your clients was murdered
in a bar

387
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:20,870
while wearing your suit.

388
00:19:21,070 --> 00:19:21,740
Murder?

389
00:19:23,910 --> 00:19:25,070
Someone died?

390
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:26,460
It was that serious?

391
00:19:28,630 --> 00:19:29,670
My store

392
00:19:30,430 --> 00:19:32,350
doesn't cater to anyone.

393
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:35,190
Liu Ang clearly didn't belong here.

394
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:38,260
Did he buy more

395
00:19:38,430 --> 00:19:40,020
than one suit from you?

396
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:41,350
Let me check the records.

397
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:45,220
If I remember right, he ordered
at least seven or eight shirts.

398
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:47,110
And more suits.

399
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:51,110
Did he pay for all of them himself?

400
00:19:51,110 --> 00:19:52,300
Depends on how you look at it.

401
00:19:55,430 --> 00:19:56,300
What do you mean?

402
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:03,070
Mr. K,

403
00:20:04,190 --> 00:20:06,390
just get to the point already.

404
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:07,630
We're friends

405
00:20:07,630 --> 00:20:08,780
and there are no outsiders.

406
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:09,980
Back then,

407
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:11,630
my dad had ordered suits from you

408
00:20:11,630 --> 00:20:13,110
before you even had this shop.

409
00:20:13,780 --> 00:20:15,910
Just tell us.

410
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:19,940
Mister,

411
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:22,110
your ring looks unique.

412
00:20:23,430 --> 00:20:24,590
This?

413
00:20:25,190 --> 00:20:26,700
Looks like a ring, doesn't it?

414
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:29,670
It's actually a thimble
I've been used for years.

415
00:20:30,740 --> 00:20:32,220
Tailors like us

416
00:20:32,390 --> 00:20:33,940
can only wear thimbles on our fingers.

417
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:40,190
Give me a moment.

418
00:20:40,390 --> 00:20:41,430
I'll check the records.

419
00:20:50,910 --> 00:20:53,020
Here are all the client records.

420
00:20:57,260 --> 00:21:00,380
(K Tailoring Purchase Records)

421
00:21:00,390 --> 00:21:02,590
Liu Ang first came
to my store four years ago.

422
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:04,220
What I remember is,

423
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:05,740
every time he visited,

424
00:21:06,070 --> 00:21:07,780
he brought a different woman.

425
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,670
Thisâ€¦ This is too expensive.

426
00:21:17,670 --> 00:21:18,500
Maybe another one.

427
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:19,910
If I want to prove my sincerity,

428
00:21:19,910 --> 00:21:20,910
what's a little money?

429
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:25,670
All right. Just a moment.

430
00:21:25,670 --> 00:21:26,260
Okay.

431
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,700
(Q: Did you say in the bar
you'd kill him?)
